OL,3,CMan defrauded people out of thousands
OL,4,Cfor 'designer handbags', court hears
OL,6,FA man who claimed to be a millionaire
OL,7,Fdefrauded people out of thousands of
OL,8,Fpounds which he promised would be used
OL,9,Fto buy and sell designer handbags, a
OL,10,Fcourt has heard.
OL,12,FJack Watkin, 26, is alleged to have
OL,13,Foffered a business opportunity to
OL,14,Fpeople who would loan him large sums
OL,15,Fof money, with the promise it would be
OL,16,Fused to buy exclusive Hermes handbags
OL,17,Fhe would sell on at profit.
