OL,3,CMan defrauded people out of thousands
OL,4,Cfor 'designer handbags', court hears
OL,6,FOpening his trial at Chester Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Friday, 20 June, Matthew
OL,8,FKerruish-Jones, prosecuting, told the
OL,9,Fjury: "This case is about handbags."
OL,11,FHe said Watkin defrauded six
OL,12,Fcomplainants out of sums, including
OL,13,Fhis father, Jason Watkin, who loaned
OL,14,Fhim more than #29,000.
OL,16,FHe said: "The defendant put forward
OL,17,Fthe outward facade of a glamorous and
OL,18,Fluxurious lifestyle.
