OL,6,F"This, it seems, engendered trust and
OL,7,Fled a number of individuals to loan
OL,8,Fhim large sums of money on the promise
OL,9,Fof either a financial return, or
OL,10,Fluxury items. Neither of which
OL,11,Fmaterialised."
OL,13,FHe said complainants would be left
OL,14,F"out of pocket for large sums of
OL,15,Fmoney".
OL,17,FHe added: "The defendant would make
OL,18,Fexcuses and avoid the complainants,
OL,19,Fall the while spending large sums of
OL,20,Fmoney on maintaining his seemingly
OL,21,Flavish lifestyle."
