OL,3,CMan defrauded people out of thousands
OL,4,Cfor 'designer handbags', court hears
OL,6,FThe jury was told bag purchases from
OL,7,FHermes were only allowed to select
OL,8,Fregistered customers and, because of
OL,9,Ftheir exclusivity, the bags often
OL,10,Fattracted a value far in excess of
OL,11,Ftheir original price when resold.
OL,13,FThe court heard Jason Watkin loaned
OL,14,Fhis son money in 2019 after he
OL,15,Fapproached him with a business
OL,16,Fproposition.
OL,18,FHe was not repaid, but could see from
OL,19,Fsocial media his son was "spending
OL,20,Flavishly on his lifestyle", the jury
OL,21,Fwas told.
