OL,3,CMan defrauded people out of thousands
OL,4,Cfor 'designer handbags', court hears
OL,6,FMr Kerruish-Jones said: "For the next
OL,7,Fyear or so, Mr Watkin repeatedly asked
OL,8,Ffor his money back. He was
OL,9,Fincreasingly concerned that his money
OL,10,Fhad not been used to purchase a bag
OL,11,Fbut had in fact gone to the defendant
OL,12,Ffunding his lifestyle."
OL,14,FThe jury was told Watkin approached
OL,15,FChristine Colbert, who resold designer
OL,16,Fbags and clothing through her
OL,17,FPrestbury shop Dress Cheshire, in 2020
OL,18,Fand told her his name was Jack Holding.
