OL,3,CMan defrauded people out of thousands
OL,4,Cfor 'designer handbags', court hears
OL,6,FMs Colbert loaned the defendant a
OL,7,Ftotal of #91,000 between July 2021 and
OL,8,FNovember 2022 but he only paid back
OL,9,F#47,200, the court heard.
OL,11,FHe is also alleged to have stolen two
OL,12,Fhandbags, a blue Hermes bag valued at
OL,13,F#21,000 and a Goyard bag worth #8,000,
OL,14,Ffrom Ms Colbert.
OL,16,FThe court heard Hannah Jakes had been
OL,17,Ffriends with Watkin for more than 10
OL,18,Fyears and loaned him a total of
OL,19,F#321,800, but was only repaid #88,300.
