OL,3,CMan defrauded people out of thousands
OL,4,Cfor 'designer handbags', court hears
OL,6,FMs Jakes got in touch with Ms Colbert
OL,7,Fin 2024 after seeing an Instagram post
OL,8,Fand it became clear he had defrauded
OL,9,Fthem both in a similar way, Mr
OL,10,FKerruish-Jones said.
OL,12,FFollowing their discussions, Ms Jakes
OL,13,Farranged to meet the defendant and Ms
OL,14,FColbert called the police, leading to
OL,15,Fhis arrest.
OL,17,FThe jury was told another of the
OL,18,Fcomplainants was Andor Farkas, who
OL,19,Fworked as a barman in Harrods where
OL,20,FWatkin was a regular customer.
