OL,3,CMan defrauded people out of thousands
OL,4,Cfor 'designer handbags', court hears
OL,6,FAs well as loaning him #1,000 in cash
OL,7,Fand transferring him #3,000, Mr Farkas
OL,8,Fallowed Watkin to use his credit card
OL,9,Fto borrow about #10,000, it is alleged.
OL,11,FMr Kerruish-Jones said Mr Farkar
OL,12,Ftrusted Watkin due to his assurances
OL,13,Fhe was a millionaire.
OL,15,FThe court heard Naheem Akhtar, who
OL,16,Fgave #840 to Watkin for a pair of Lora
OL,17,FPiana shoes which he never received,
OL,18,Fsaid the defendant gave the perception
OL,19,Fon social media that he was a
OL,20,Fmillionaire and involved in the
OL,21,Ffashion industry.
