OL,3,CMan defrauded people out of thousands
OL,4,Cfor 'designer handbags', court hears
OL,6,FJames Irlam, who allegedly lost
OL,7,F#65,500 to the defendant, was told by
OL,8,FWatkin he had a personal relationship
OL,9,Fwith the director of Hermes and was
OL,10,Fable to source handbags, the jury was
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,FHe agreed to loan him money after
OL,14,Fbuying a Hermes Birkin bag for #11,500
OL,15,Ffrom Watkin as a present for his
OL,16,Fwife's birthday.
OL,18,FWatkin, of Alderley Edge, Cheshire,
OL,19,Fdenies seven counts of fraud and two
OL,20,Fcounts of theft.
